t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff5d6ef elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"ff5d6ef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5083b95 elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"5083b95\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-532375f elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-accordion\" data-id=\"532375f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-accordion.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >\n        <div class=\"elementskit-accordion accoedion-primary\" id=\"accordion-6a39f73353a57\">\n\n            \n                <div class=\"elementskit-card active\">\n                    <div class=\"elementskit-card-header\" id=\"primaryHeading-0-532375f\">\n                        <a href=\"#Collapse-6f491396a39f73353a57\" class=\"ekit-accordion--toggler elementskit-btn-link collapsed\" data-ekit-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#Collapse-6f491396a39f73353a57\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"Collapse-6f491396a39f73353a57\">\n                                                            <div class=\"ekit_accordion_icon_left_group\">\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_normal_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Normal Icon -->\n                                        <i class=\"mdi mdi-plus\"></i>                                    </div>\n\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_active_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Active Icon -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"icofont icofont-minus\"></i>                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n\n                            \n                            <span class=\"ekit-accordion-title\">How does MBBS in Vietnam assist students in pursuing their MBBS aspirations?</span>\n\n                            \n                                                    </a>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div id=\"Collapse-6f491396a39f73353a57\" class=\" show collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"primaryHeading-0-532375f\" data-parent=\"#accordion-6a39f73353a57\">\n\n                        <div class=\"elementskit-card-body ekit-accordion--content\">\n                            <p>MBBS in Vietnam is a comprehensive resource that offers guidance and support at every stage of your medical career, including admission, visa, and travel assistance, as well as ongoing support throughout the completion of your course.</p>                        </div>\n\n                    </div>\n\n                </div><!-- .elementskit-card END -->\n\n                \n                <div class=\"elementskit-card \">\n                    <div class=\"elementskit-card-header\" id=\"primaryHeading-1-532375f\">\n                        <a href=\"#Collapse-042b3786a39f73353a57\" class=\"ekit-accordion--toggler elementskit-btn-link collapsed\" data-ekit-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#Collapse-042b3786a39f73353a57\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"Collapse-042b3786a39f73353a57\">\n                                                            <div class=\"ekit_accordion_icon_left_group\">\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_normal_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Normal Icon -->\n                                        <i class=\"mdi mdi-plus\"></i>                                    </div>\n\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_active_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Active Icon -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"icofont icofont-minus\"></i>                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n\n                            \n                            <span class=\"ekit-accordion-title\">What factors should be considered when selecting a medical college, and how can MBBS in Vietnam help?</span>\n\n                            \n                                                    </a>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div id=\"Collapse-042b3786a39f73353a57\" class=\" collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"primaryHeading-1-532375f\" data-parent=\"#accordion-6a39f73353a57\">\n\n                        <div class=\"elementskit-card-body ekit-accordion--content\">\n                            <p>MBBS in Vietnam can guide in selecting a suitable medical college by considering multiple factors, including academic reputation, accreditation, infrastructure, faculty qualifications, clinical exposure, and feedback from students.</p>                        </div>\n\n                    </div>\n\n                </div><!-- .elementskit-card END -->\n\n                \n                <div class=\"elementskit-card \">\n                    <div class=\"elementskit-card-header\" id=\"primaryHeading-2-532375f\">\n                        <a href=\"#Collapse-fcc8da46a39f73353a57\" class=\"ekit-accordion--toggler elementskit-btn-link collapsed\" data-ekit-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#Collapse-fcc8da46a39f73353a57\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"Collapse-fcc8da46a39f73353a57\">\n                                                            <div class=\"ekit_accordion_icon_left_group\">\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_normal_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Normal Icon -->\n                                        <i class=\"mdi mdi-plus\"></i>                                    </div>\n\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_active_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Active Icon -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"icofont icofont-minus\"></i>                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n\n                            \n                            <span class=\"ekit-accordion-title\">What important aspects should be considered before choosing a university, and how can MBBS in Vietnam guide in this regard?</span>\n\n                            \n                                                    </a>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div id=\"Collapse-fcc8da46a39f73353a57\" class=\" collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"primaryHeading-2-532375f\" data-parent=\"#accordion-6a39f73353a57\">\n\n                        <div class=\"elementskit-card-body ekit-accordion--content\">\n                            <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Before selecting a university, it\u2019s essential to consider factors like the university\u2019s recognition, curriculum, clinical training opportunities, student support services, and overall reputation. MBBS in Vietnam can provide valuable insights and guidance to help you make an informed decision.</span></p>                        </div>\n\n                    </div>\n\n                </div><!-- .elementskit-card END -->\n\n                \n                <div class=\"elementskit-card \">\n                    <div class=\"elementskit-card-header\" id=\"primaryHeading-3-532375f\">\n                        <a href=\"#Collapse-247bb1b6a39f73353a57\" class=\"ekit-accordion--toggler elementskit-btn-link collapsed\" data-ekit-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#Collapse-247bb1b6a39f73353a57\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"Collapse-247bb1b6a39f73353a57\">\n                                                            <div class=\"ekit_accordion_icon_left_group\">\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_normal_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Normal Icon -->\n                                        <i class=\"mdi mdi-plus\"></i>                                    </div>\n\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_active_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Active Icon -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"icofont icofont-minus\"></i>                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n\n                            \n                            <span class=\"ekit-accordion-title\">Is it necessary to learn the local language for an MBBS course, and can MBBS in Vietnam assist in finding language learning resources?</span>\n\n                            \n                                                    </a>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div id=\"Collapse-247bb1b6a39f73353a57\" class=\" collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"primaryHeading-3-532375f\" data-parent=\"#accordion-6a39f73353a57\">\n\n                        <div class=\"elementskit-card-body ekit-accordion--content\">\n                            <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">MBBS in Vietnam can help you with language proficiencies. The most frequently used language is English, which is required for patient communication.</span></p>                        </div>\n\n                    </div>\n\n                </div><!-- .elementskit-card END -->\n\n                \n                <div class=\"elementskit-card \">\n                    <div class=\"elementskit-card-header\" id=\"primaryHeading-4-532375f\">\n                        <a href=\"#Collapse-43386d36a39f73353a57\" class=\"ekit-accordion--toggler elementskit-btn-link collapsed\" data-ekit-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#Collapse-43386d36a39f73353a57\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"Collapse-43386d36a39f73353a57\">\n                                                            <div class=\"ekit_accordion_icon_left_group\">\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_normal_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Normal Icon -->\n                                        <i class=\"mdi mdi-plus\"></i>                                    </div>\n\n                                    <div class=\"ekit_accordion_active_icon\">\n                                        <!-- Active Icon -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"icofont icofont-minus\"></i>                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n\n                            \n                            <span class=\"ekit-accordion-title\">Are there Indian lecturers at universities offering MBBS courses, and how can MBBS in Vietnam provide information on faculty composition?</span>\n\n                            \n                                                    </a>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div id=\"Collapse-43386d36a39f73353a57\" class=\" collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"primaryHeading-4-532375f\" data-parent=\"#accordion-6a39f73353a57\">\n\n                        <div class=\"elementskit-card-body ekit-accordion--content\">\n                            <p>Numerous universities have a diverse pool of faculty members, which may include Indian educators, who contribute their skills and expertise to enrich the educational environment. MBBS in Vietnam can furnish detailed insights into faculty composition at these universities.</p>                        </div>\n\n                    </div>\n\n                </div><!-- .elementskit-card END -->\n\n                                        </div>\n    </div>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\n</main>"
